Installation - Actually: creation of Debian binary packages
-----------------------------------------------------------

0.  Rename directory to suit Debian conventions

1.  Untar the latest source tarballs for: 

	jpeg-mmx, libmovtar, quicktime4linux and mjpegtools

	OR:

    Get the latest CVS versions.

2.  Rename the directories to the *above* names 

	(get rid of the version numbers etc!).

3.  aclocal
    autoconf
    automake --add-missing

    You'll need to build the ./configure files for the sub-directories
    if you used the CVS version...

    ./configure
    make

